Date: 1 Aug 2001 22:02:48 -0400
From: Keath L Marx, DVM <xoticdvm@bellatlantic.net>

Just a quick note to correct an error. This organism has been reclassified
and renamed (a year ago?) to _Chlamydophilia psittaci_ along with many of
the strains affecting other species such as _Chlamydophilia felis_, etc.
--
Keath L Marx, DVM
Seven Seas Veterinary Services
Blacksburg, VA USA
Co-Author - Exotic Animal Drug Compendium
<http://exoticanimal.net>
